{"tid":1416382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於之後嘅行動睇法同想講下自己睇法","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:02:49.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80a9136e06be3195b4cee7d1d9dded799529346d","tid":1416382,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"今日777記者會之後所引發嘅衝突我首先要強烈譴責<br />\n<br />\n冇錯 777 係想將呢兩個月嘅衝突變成所謂嘅&quot;警民衝突&quot;<br />\n但係人都話要對準政權唔好再攻擊差老(721前嘅言論)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>你地冇無失焦 因為777一直企係警隊後面</strong><br />\n而警隊又係呢個政權嘅前線 由6月幾開始一直都係攻擊緊政權<br />\n<br />\n<strong>你FF下 呀淋病佢渣住個叫&quot;警隊&quot;嘅盾</strong><br />\n破其盾 咁佢就赤裸裸對住你 到時你想點就點 (排除中共發難出共軍)<br />\n如仲死不認錯 就立即建立臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n而點樣整冧呢盾 請自行再討論  (架空特區政府)<br />\n同天琦講過 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要被仇恨支配自己</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab7d0035b8012b84956f9e77af3e94f788ac129","tid":1416382,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544f88be4f7cefbd7f1365466babb34aca26a4c4","tid":1416382,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9792110bf41e9f51971eaca11ff01ab3002ed913","tid":1416382,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor